DESCRIPTION:Are you ready to laugh your Pantz off? This comedy sketch show 
 combines physical comedy and cleverly written script with some bizarre twis
 ts to make you do just that. Created and performed by actor and comedian Ma
 ry Redmond\, this is a character-led comedy sketch show that uses cinematic
  voice over and mime to immerse you in each of their worlds. With certain c
 haracters reappearing throughout\, you will unfortunately have the privileg
 e of getting to know them\, perhaps a little too much\, as you start to unr
 avel and understand their slightly dark and tragic lives. With years of tri
 ed and tested material\, plus fresh new treats\, this is the alternative co
 medy show you didn’t know you desperately needed. Your pantz will not sur
 vive it.\nMore info: https://comedyatlas.app/comedy-atlas/event/maz-pantz/
